# Datastar Signal Dependency Graph Demo
Output demo/signal-graph.gif
Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Padding 10
Set Theme "Kanagawa"

Type "nvim -u demo/tapes/init.lua test-drive.html"
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Run the signal graph command
Type ":DatastarSignalGraph"
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Let user see the full graph
Sleep 3s

# Close the split
Type ":close"
Enter
Sleep 1s
